dc_creator_sm: New Jersey. Department of Environmental Protection
dc_description_s: This data is a graphical representation of the Merged Inventory Historic Properties of New Jersey. This data includes only those historic properties and sites that are included in the New Jersey or National Registers of Historic Places, or that have been determined Eligible for inclusion through federal or state processes as administered by the New Jersey Historic Preservation Office (HPO).  Inclusion in this data set does not preclude the existence of other historic properties or sites not within this category or as yet unidentified.THIS DATA REPRESENTS ONLY A PORTION OF THE TOTAL NUMBER OF REGISTERED OR ELIGIBLE HISTORIC PROPERTIES IN NEW JERSEY. THE HPO IS STILL IN THE PROCESS BUILDING THIS COVERAGE. (See Completeness Report)
